{
  "stem": "3835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, your mother gave me all the [NON-ENGLISH] from the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the gold, and the jewelry, the diamonds, she didn't give me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Ah, you hear that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was the way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She didn't give me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had such beautiful earrings and-- and her rings-- she didn't give me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She gave me all the [NON-ENGLISH] from the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, give-- I would like to have a couple of shirts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm sorry, I have nothing for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was the point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't-- naturally, from time to times, if they didn't behave, they punished them too, but only if they did something wrong.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this was in '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, in '42, it starts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the middle of '42, I start to-- we start to hear that they are burning Jews, that there is a Treblinka and an Auschwitz, and that they are burning Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of Jews didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a lot did believe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, they started the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] surrounding the ghettos and taking them at the railroads to the-- to the station, taking them with the railroad to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we start hearing this town was taken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This town was taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Our town was not taken yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I'm sure they will take from our town too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because from the small towns around Ostrowiec, all the Jews they pushed into Ostrowiec-- they should have them together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like, from 5,000, 6,000 Jews, suddenly, in '42, we had about 15,000 Jews in our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, I believed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And how I believed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number one, I was pessimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't an optimist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't believe that God is going to save me if I'm not going to save myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was always pessimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
